@startuml proxy_runtime_updates
title Runtime Updates After Proxy is Connected to ConfigDaemon

participant "PollingThread" as PollingThread
participant "InternalConfigProviderProxy" as ICP
participant "ARA::COM" as CD
participant "ConfigProviderImpl" as CPImpl
participant "Persistency" as Persist
participant "KVS" as KVS
participant "ClientApplication" as App

note over PollingThread, ICP: Polling thread running (interval: 5 seconds default)

== Periodic Update Detection ==

loop Every polling_cycle_interval
    PollingThread -> PollingThread: Wake up (timer or on-demand trigger)
    PollingThread -> ICP: GetNewSamples(LastUpdatedParameterSet)
    ICP -> CD: mw::com GetNewSamples
    CD --> ICP: ["SetA", "SetB"]
    ICP --> PollingThread: Updated parameter set names

    loop For each updated set name
        PollingThread -> CPImpl: LastUpdatedParameterSetReceiveHandler(set_name)

        == Step 1: Fetch Updated ParameterSet ==

        CPImpl -> ICP: GetParameterSet(set_name, timeout)
        ICP -> CD: mw::com GetParameterSet
        CD --> ICP: Updated ParameterSet (JSON + qualifier)
        ICP --> CPImpl: ParameterSet

        == Step 2: Write to Persistency ==

        CPImpl -> Persist: CacheParameterSet(param_set, sync=true)

        alt ParameterSet is kQualified
            Persist -> Persist: NeedToPersist() returns true
            Persist -> Persist: ContainsSameContent() check

            alt Content changed
                Persist -> KVS: set("CfgP__SetName", JSON)
                note over KVS: Immediate sync (sync_to_storage=true)
            else Content unchanged
                note over Persist: Skip write - content identical
            end
        else ParameterSet not kQualified
            note over Persist: Skip - only qualified sets persisted
        end

        == Step 3: Update In-Memory Cache ==

        CPImpl -> CPImpl: Update parameter_sets_[set_name]
        note over CPImpl: Atomically replace shared_ptr\nThread-safe update

        == Step 4: Notify Application Callbacks ==

        alt Client registered callback for this set
            CPImpl -> App: OnChangedParameterSet callback(set_name)
            note over App: Application processes update
        end
    end
end

@enduml
